                        <interp inst="t18540918-name-174" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE SCOTT</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City-policeman</hi>). I was on duty on London—bridge, on the morning of 30th Aug., about half past eleven o'clock—I saw the prisoner there—I saw him go up to a lady, and put his left hand into her pocket, and as soon as he pulled his hand out of her pocket he put both his hands toge<lb></lb>ther—I took hold of both his hands; I took this purse from his hand—I spoke to the prosecutrix.</p>
